        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_4903c438">
            <lb />Be Sure and See the First Showing
            <lb />of the new
            <lb />Welte Straight Grand
            <lb />the <name type="brand">Original Welte Mignon
            <lb />Reproducing Grand</name>
            <lb />with Reproducing Action Invisibly Installed
            <lb />and the <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon Musicale</name>
            <lb />an electrically operated attachment to
            the original <name type="brand">Welte-
            <lb />Mignon</name> piano which will enable one
            <seg ana="#touch_of_a_button" resp="#np" type="topic">
                merely by pressing a button
            </seg>
            <lb />to hear any of ten compositions from a repertoire
            <lb />of one's own selections.
            <lb />in the following period models
            <lb /><name type="brand">FLORENTINE GRAND</name>
            <lb /><name type="brand">LOUIS XVI GRAND</name>
            <lb /><name type="brand">GEORGIAN WELTE-MIGNON</name>
            <lb /><name type="brand">COLONIAL</name> (with the <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon Musicale</name>)
            <lb /><name type="brand">LOUIS XV WELTE-MIGNON</name>
            <lb />and working models of the Welte Actions
            <lb />Now Displayed in
            <address>
                Suite 1710-1712-1714
                <lb />HOTEL COMMODORE
            </address>
            <lb /><orgName>WELTE-MIGNON CORPORATION</orgName>
            <lb /><persName>WILLIAM C. HEATON</persName>, Wholesale Manager, Piano
